### ChatApp API Testing

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5187/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Đăng ký
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "passwordHash": "123456"
}

### 2. Đăng nhập
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "passwordHash": "123456"
}

### 3. Lấy danh sách users (cần token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Lấy danh sách rooms và DMs (cần token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/room
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Tạo room mới (cần token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/room
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "General",
  "description": "Room chat chung"
}

### 6. Tham gia room (cần token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/room/1/join
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Tạo/get DM với user (cần token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/room/dm/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Lấy tin nhắn trong room (cần token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/message/room/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Gửi tin nhắn trong room (cần token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/message
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello world!",
  "roomId": 1
}

### 10. Gửi tin nhắn DM (cần token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/message
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello private!",
  "receiverId": 2
}
